 r←CheckLookIn;andif;msg
⍝ Checks whether the string in "LookIn" points to a namespace or script (0) or not (1).
⍝ In case it is empty it becomes `#`
 r←0
 :If 0=n.ReuseSearch.State
 :AndIf 9≠⎕NC n.LookIn.Text
     :If r←0=≢n.LookIn.Text
         n.LookIn.Text←'#'
     :ElseIf (,'#')≢,n.LookIn.Text
     :AndIf '⎕SE'≢##.A.Uppercase n.LookIn.Text
         {}##.Question.ShowMsg'Start looking here: "',n.LookIn.Text,'¨ does not exist'
         r←1
     :EndIf
 :EndIf
